{"tid":588193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"犯民保皇根本一家親","createTime":"2018-03-11T04:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T05:10:56.000Z","uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1ab43828570f80d2ba35182abd18176d054bb1","tid":588193,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:51:40.000Z","msg":"話投白票係益保皇按道理根本就唔成立，白票代表冇一個參選人可以代表你個人意願，你地都含左廿年大局已定，重諗住靠今次補選話畀人知我地係香港人不願低頭？上次呢？上次唔係補選？你玩鳩我呀？<br />\n<br />\n含撚含左廿年口爆埋吞撚埋，溫水煮蛙煮到熟撚晒先知仆街，你地冇撚野呀，要醒早就醒左啦（醒撚埋右），唔好問我依家醒點解唔得，我問返08年你地做緊乜"},{"pid":"a69150076bf0b9184abe1766e0a9f78e23e63d88","tid":588193,"uid":49456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/114753_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F114753_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4b819587&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b473bcdb20b75cc9770fa13e4ffd05e77a41900","tid":588193,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"由犯民踏入中聯辦個刻你地就已經畀犯民出賣，劇本亦寫好晒，你地所謂嘅票只係永續含撚最黑暗<br />\n就好似工賊會咁日日話保障工人權益乜乜乜<br />\n實際就陰乾班豬兜，好彩係班豬兜金魚記憶，第二日工賊會掛一掛banner就乜事都冇發生"},{"pid":"b9633b8b7d19bc915ad7b9751072655107edb174","tid":588193,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"華人賤種"},{"pid":"bdc7a8566ac8ea1e27189453524cc1c763bb9ad3","tid":588193,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a69150076bf0b9184abe1766e0a9f78e23e63d88","tid":588193,"uid":49456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/114753_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F114753_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4b819587&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"唔撚理啦，港柒應有此報，黃皮狗走難民族基因圖譜已經講左個未來係點行"},{"pid":"01c24324bdaa3cbb5e82f12c9767984daa6b1cd1","tid":588193,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"閪港種就係賤 就係屌唔醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}